        <head>13</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>13 years of Depression</l>
          <l>13 years for this burning ground</l>
          <l>13 years to my dying nation</l>
          <l>Let my people go</l>
          <l>13 years where we breathing fire</l>
          <l>13 years full of brothers hate</l>
          <l>13 years that are going nowhere</l>
          <l>Nowhere my heart sets</l>
          <l>Forgive us for the madness we don’t know what to</l>
          <l>For every road we’ve taken</l>
          <l>We could not find a passage through</l>
          <l>All eyes on us but they don’t seem to realize</l>
          <l>You cannot fight to conquer when your you’re fighting for your life</l>
          <l>And for the love of my people for the love of my land</l>
          <l>I hope their hunger can handle all they have been fed</l>
          <l>So let us hear the silence let us turn the page</l>
          <l>Unpleasant melodies of a generation’s rage</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
